0defenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20salvo%20on%20Tuesday%20involved%20at%20least%2042%20hits%20from%20Shahed%20drones%2C%20alongside%20six%20missile%20strikes%2C%20the%20Ukrainian%20Air%20Force%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-break-record-nearly-thousand-shahed-strike-drones-single-day-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774411316000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c350685b58f1f0f9336e12%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-break-record-nearly-thousand-shahed-strike-drones-single-day-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ukraine%20said%20it%20shot%20down%20906%20out%20of%20948%20long-range%20drones%20launched%20into%20its%20borders%20within%20a%20single%2024-hour%20window.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mloh%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Loh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-break-record-nearly-thousand-shahed-strike-drones-single-day-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cognizant%20TN%20headcount%20down%20by%2010%2C000%3B%20hiring%20shifts%20to%20emerging%20cities%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774411301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129790977%2Cimgsize-33524.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fcognizant-tn-headcount-down-by-10000-hiring-shifts-to-emerging-cities%2Farticleshow%2F129790982.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cognizant's%20Tamil%20Nadu%20delivery%20center%20headcount%20has%20dropped%20by%2010%2C000%20employees%20as%20hiring%20shifts%20to%20cities%20like%20Indore%20and%20Bhubaneswar.%20While%20Chennai%20remains%20its%20largest%20Indian%20hub%2C%20the%20company%20is%20expanding%20in%20Visakhapatnam%2C%20investing%20Rs%201%