s%20absurd.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECreative%20jobs%20are%20rarely%20supported%20in%20mainstream%20Indian%20households.%20Both%20my%20parents%20come%20from%20very%20rural%20backgrounds%2C%20having%20settled%20in%20a%20larger%20town%20to%20give%20my%20siblings%20and%20me%20a%20comfortable%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%2010%20years%20in%20law%20school%2C%20research%2C%20and%20consulting%2C%20I%20decided%20I%20wanted%20a%20life%20I%20enjoyed%20rather%20than%20one%20spent%20living%20for%20the%20weekends.%20Last%20year%2C%20I%20quit%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkpmg-big-four-junior-consultants-manage-teams-ai-agents-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ejob%20at%20KPMG%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20moved%20from%20Singapore%20to%20Mumbai%20to%20be%20a%20full-time%20writer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2204c96ca8-e1b4-4cf6-a999-7f886b59a93b%5C%22%3EMany%20career%20pivots%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Namrata%20Yadav's%20corporate%20card%20at%20KPMG.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6965f9e504eda4732f2ef375%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYadav%20tried%20many%20career%20paths%20before%20quitting%20corporate%20for%20life%20as%20a%20full-time%20writer.%3Cp%3ENamrata%20Yadav%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20taken%20many%20career%20pivots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20my%20law%20bachelor's%20degree%20in%20India%2C%20I%20pursued%20a%20master's%20program%20in%20international%20relations%20at%20the%20National%20University%20of%20Singapore%20from%202019%20to%202021%2C%20and%20then%20worked%20as%20a%20research%20analyst%20at%20the%20university%20for%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20never%20worked%20in%20corporate%20before%2C%20so%20I%20moved%20to%20KPMG%20in%202022%20to%20try%20a%20consulting%20role%20and%20work%20at%20a%20big%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20work%20culture%20was%20decent%2C%20and%20I%20earned%20a%20stable%20annual%20salary%20of%20around%2057%2C000%20Singapore%20dollars%2C%20or%20about%20%2444%2C500.%20Singapore%20is%20an%20expensive%20city%20%E2%80%94%20I%20was%20spending%20up%20to%20SG%243%2C200%20a%20month%20on%20expenses%2C%20including%20rent%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20didn't%20feel%20stretched%20thin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20quickly%20realized%20I%20was%20too%20right-brained%20for%20the%20job%2C%20and%20that%20corporate%20life%20did%20not%20feel%20right%20for%20me.%20The%20hours%20were%20long%20and%20demanding.%20I%20didn't%20want%20my%20weekend%20to%20be%20an%20escape%20from%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgreat-lock-in-no-excuses-just-grind-hustle-culture-productivity-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E40-hour%20workweek%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20writing%20religiously%20when%20I%20moved%20to%20Singapore%2C%20and%20only%20in%20Hindi%20%E2%80%94%20I%20think%20it%20was%20just%20the%20anxiety%20of%20being%20in%20a%20new%20country.%20I%20wrote%2C%20and%20still%20write%2C%20about%20relationships%2C%20family%2C%20friendships%2C%20love%2C%20and%20everyday%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20during%20my%20stint%20at%20KPMG%2C%20I%20felt%20I%20could%20not%20devote%20enough%20time%20to%20writing%2C%20which%20led%20me%20to%20think%20that%20creative%20work%20was%20my%20calling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f650fa96-3823-491e-96b8-8a40a4134175%5C%22%3EThe%20final%20straw%20and%20the%20big%20move%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22767%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Namrata%20Yadav%20writing%20in%20nature.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6965fa3e64858d02d2183a5b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22575%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYadav%20moved%20to%20Mumbai%20in%202025%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20writing.%3Cp%3ENamrata%20Yadav%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20enjoying%20the%20work%20I%20was%20doing%20at%20KPMG%20made%20me%20think%20about%20what%20I%20truly%20enjoy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202024%2C%20I%20was%20selected%20to%20perform%20my%20spoken%20word%20poetry%20at%20a%20literature%20festival%20in%20Lucknow%2C%20India.%20Watching%20the%20festival%2C%20I%20decided%20that%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20envy%20these%20people%20who%20get%20to%20have%20an%20hour%20onstage%20and%20entertain%20us.%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20when%20I%20came%20back%20to%20Singapore%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20wrap%20up%20and%20move%20back%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmumbai-mistakes-first-time-visitors-make-from-india-local-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoved%20to%20Mumbai%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20game%20plan%3A%20Get%20a%20job%20that%20can%20sustain%20me%20once%20my%20savings%20dry%20up%2C%20but%20is%20not%20too%20demanding%2C%20so%20I%20can%20focus%20on%20writing.%20But%20after%20a%20few%20job%20interviews%2C%20I%20realized%20I%20really%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinance-sophomore-started-booming-side-hustle-making-curry-puffs-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edidn't%20want%20another%20desk%20job%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMumbai's%20an%20expensive%20city.%20I%20live%20in%20a%20shared%20flat%20with%20two%20other%20creatives%20in%20Andheri%20West%2C%20one%20of%20the%20epicenters%20where%20many%20writers%2C%20actors%2C%20and%20struggling%20artists%20like%20me%20live.%20I%20pay%20less%20for%20rent%20than%20in%20Singapore%20%E2%80%94%2034%2C000%20Indian%20rupees%2C%20or%20around%20%24360.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20my%20expenses%20are%20lower%20than%20in%20Singapore%2C%20having%20to%20forgo%20a%20stable%20paycheck%20and%20go%20months%20without%20earning%20anything%20has%20tested%20my%20grit.%20I'm%20banking%20on%20my%20savings%20from%20my%20corporate%20job%20in%20Singapore%20to%20keep%20me%20going%20for%20the%20next%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2205971bca-ab24-4d56-b83e-a8779bb776f1%5C%22%3EOne%20week%20till%20my%20first%20spoken-word%20show%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Namrata%20Yadav.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6965f96b764ca5f34d2a52a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENamrata%20Yadav%20said%20she's%20given%20herself%20three%20months%20to%20fully%20focus%20on%20writing%20for%20her%20first%20debut%20show.%3Cp%3ENamrata%20Yadav%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20do%20a%20solo%20debut%20show%20on%20March%2028%20and%20to%20devote%20the%20three%20months%20between%20to%20working%20on%20my%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20morning%20after%20coffee%2C%20I%20spend%20more%20than%20two%20hours%20just%20writing.%20I%20continue%20working%20on%20it%20in%20the%20afternoon%2C%20and%20have%20started%20posting%20about%20my%20process%20on%20Instagram%20to%20get%20the%20word%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20want%20to%20test%20if%20I%20have%20what%20it%20takes%20to%20become%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-6-figure-finance-job-moved-hawaii-be-writer-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20storyteller%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20to%20become%20a%20memorable%20one%20at%20that.%20Do%20I%20have%20it%20in%20me%20to%20keep%20doing%20it%20over%20and%20over%20again%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20lesson%20learned%20since%20going%20into%20poetry%20full%20time%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquiet-quitting-corporate-start-own-business-struggles-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eunlearning%20the%20corporate%20mindset%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20expecting%20a%20tangible%20outcome%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20days%2C%20I%20love%20what%20I've%20written.%20But%20on%20other%20days%2C%20it's%20not%20worth%20sharing%20with%20people.%20So%20I've%20had%20to%20be%20patient%20and%20remind