e%20billions%20under%20a%20blockbuster%20Elon-style%20pay%20package%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223197%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Andrew%20Bosworth%2C%20Meta%20CTO%2C%20is%20mid%20speech%20with%20his%20hands%20held%20aloft%20in%20front%20of%20him%2C%20as%20if%20emphasizing%20a%20point.%20He%20is%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20a%20light%20blue%20background%20and%20wearing%20a%20dark%20denim%20overshirt%2C%20which%20is%20open%20over%20a%20white%20undershirt.%20He%20is%20wearing%20a%20microphone%20on%20his%20face.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c3248f5b58f1f0f9336dae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222167%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMeta%20CTO%20Andrew%20Bosworth%20is%20one%20of%20the%20execs%20set%20for%20a%20big%20pay%20increase%2C%20if%20the%20company%20meets%20stock%20goals.%3Cp%3EJOSH%20EDELSON%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESix%20top%20Meta%20execs%20are%20set%20to%20receive%20huge%20pay%20increases%20%E2%80%94%20excluding%20CEO%20Mark%20Zuckerberg.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20that%20hinges%20on%20Meta%20meeting%20%26quot%3Bexceedingly%20aggressive%26quot%3B%20stock%20prices%20over%20five%20years%2C%20Meta%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20getting%20expensive%20to%20retain%20top%20leaders%20as%20AI%20makes%20tech%20more%20competitive%20than%20ever.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMeta's%20C-suite%20is%20set%20to%20score%20a%20big%20increase%20in%20their%20compensation%20%E2%80%94%20if%20the%20%241.5%20trillion%20tech%20company%20can%20massively%20boost%20its%20stock%20price%2C%20according%20to%20forms%20Meta%20just%20filed%20with%20the%20SEC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20forms%20detail%20a%20two-part%20incentive%20system%20for%20six%20executives%2C%20including%20CTO%20Andrew%20Bosworth%2C%20CFO%20Susan%20Li%2C%20chief%20operating%20officer%20Javier%20Olivan%2C%20and%20chief%20product%20officer%20Chris%20Cox.%20The%20execs%20are%20set%20to%20receive%20an%20increased%20number%20of%20restricted%20stock%20units%20that%20vest%20over%20time%2C%20and%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20stock%20options%20that%20give%20them%20the%20right%20to%20purchase%20shares%20at%20lofty%20future%20targets%2C%20with%20a%20deadline%20of%20March%202031.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20conversion%20price%20in%20the%20packages%20starts%20at%20%241%2C116.08%20and%20goes%20up%20to%20%243%2C727.12.%20The%20high%20end%20of%20the%20package%20would%20put%20Meta's%20market%20cap%20at%20more%20than%20%248%20trillion%2C%20based%20on%20today's%20shares%20outstanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta's%20stock%20%E2%80%94%20trading%20at%20about%20%24600%20%E2%80%94%20is%20down%20nearly%203%25%20in%20the%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBosworth%2C%20Cox%2C%20Li%2C%20and%20Olivan%20would%20receive%20the%20most%20options%2C%20which%20would%20set%20them%20up%20for%20paydays%20of%20up%20to%20%242.7%20billion%2C%20depending%20on%20how%20Meta's%20stock%20rises%20and%20how%20much%20they%20choose%20to%20exercise%20and%20at%20what%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20compensation%20package%20is%20a%20sign%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-talent-wars-recruiting-hiring-white-hot-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20AI%20talent%20wars%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20which%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthinking-machines-lab-loses-2-founding-members-to-meta-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehotter%20than%20ever%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20could%20be%20spreading%20to%20the%20C-suite%20as%20tech%20companies%20battle%20for%20AI%20supremacy.%20The%20news%20also%20comes%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-weighing-major-layoffs-as-it-pours-billions-into-ai-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMeta%20weighs%20major%20layoffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20it%20pours%20billions%20into%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20big%20bet.%20These%20pay%20packages%20will%20not%20be%20realized%20unless%20Meta%20achieves%20massive%20future%20success%2C%20benefiting%20all%20of%20our%20shareholders.%20As%20with%20all%20stock%20options%2C%20there%20is%20only%20value%20if%20the%20share%20price%20meaningfully%20exceeds%20the%20exercise%20price%2C%20and%20in%20this%20case%2C%20it%20must%20be%20on%20an%20exceedingly%20aggressive%205-year%20timeline%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Meta%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20deal%20is%20structured%20in%20a%20similar%20way%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tesla-pay-package-trillion-takeaways-succession-valuation-voting-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk's%20%241%20trillion%20pay%20package%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20gave%20the%20Tesla%20CEO%20that%20amount%20in%20stock%20over%20a%2010-year%20period%20if%20he%20sextupled%20the%20carmaker's%20market%20capitalization.%20Unlike%20that%20deal%2C%20however%2C%20Meta%20CEO%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20is%20not%20included.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20Meta%20executives%20part%20of%20the%20proposed%20increase%20are%20chief%20legal%20officer%20C.J.%20Mahoney%20and%20president%20Dina%20Powell%20McCormick.%20Chief%20accounting%20officer%20Aaron%20Anderson%20would%20receive%20about%20%243%20million%20in%20RSUs%20and%20no%20stock%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20executives%20affected%20aren't%20all%20tech-focused%2C%20the%20increase%20still%20reflects%20Meta's%20commitment%20to%20leading%20the%20AI%20world%2C%20according%20to%20a%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20has%20notched%20notable%20wins%20in%20the%20AI%20talent%20wars%2C%20recently%20hiring%20three%20researchers%20from%20high-profile%20startup%20Thinking%20Machines%20Labs%2C%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthinking-machines-lab-loses-2-founding-members-to-meta-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20even%20poaching%20its%20CTO%20the%20year%2