20to%20convert%20into%20a%20flat%20bed%20big%20enough%20for%20two%20adults%20and%20a%20small%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20same%20idea%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairlines-have-lie-flat-beds-in-economy-class-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BSkycouch%26quot%3B%20on%20Air%20New%20Zealand%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20of%20United's%20Star%20Alliance%20partners.%20Other%20global%20carriers%20offer%20similar%20bed-like%20seating%20in%20economy%20by%20blocking%20entire%20rows%20so%20passengers%20can%20lie%20across%20them%2C%20but%20few%20have%20adjustable%20legrests%20to%20widen%20the%20sleeping%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20Skycouch%2C%20United's%20Relax%20Row%2C%20which%20can%20also%20be%20booked%20by%20a%20solo%20person%20or%20a%20duo%2C%20comes%20with%20several%20special%20amenities%3A%20a%20custom-fitted%20mattress%2C%20a%20plush%20blanket%2C%20and%20two%20extra%20pillows.%20Families%20get%20a%20stuffed%20toy%20and%20kid's%20travel%20kit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnited%20said%20that%20up%20to%2012%20Relax%20Rows%2C%20located%20between%20the%20economy%20and%20premium%20economy%20sections%2C%20will%20be%20featured%20on%20over%20200%20Boeing%20777%20and%20Boeing%20787%20aircraft%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20how%20much%20the%20upgrade%20will%20cost%20or%20what%20routes%20it%20will%20be%20available%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20rendering%20of%20a%20red%20headed%20woman%20stretched%20out%20on%20the%20Relax%20Row%20with%20her%20laptop.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c323eb5b58f1f0f9336da6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22852%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20%26quot%3BRelax%20Row%26quot%3B%20would%20offer%20one%20of%20the%20best%20perks%20of%20business%20class%20in%20economy.%3Cp%3EUnited%20Airlines%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Relax%20Row%20is%20another%20example%20of%20how%20United%20is%20catering%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-stock-premium-travel-demand-revenue-earnings-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epassengers%20willing%20to%20pay%20more%20for%20comfort%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20don't%20need%20the%20caviar%20or%20expensive%20bubbly%20of%20business%20class.%20The%20carrier%20reported%20an%2011%25%20increase%20in%20premium%20revenue%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCustomers%20traveling%20in%20United%20Economy%20on%20long-haul%20flights%20deserve%20an%20option%20for%20more%20space%20and%20comfort%2C%20and%20this%20is%20one%20way%20we%20can%20deliver%20that%20for%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Andrew%20Nocella%2C%20United's%20EVP%20and%20Chief%20Commercial%20Officer%2C%20said%20in%20a%20Tuesday%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Relax%20Row%20complements%20United's%20premium-economy%20offering%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fupgrading-premium-plus-united-long-flight-international-iworth-it-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPremium%20Plus%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20features%20a%20reclining%20lounger%2C%20elevated%20meals%2C%20and%20a%20leg%20and%20footrest%2C%20but%20is%20more%20expensive%20than%20regular%20coach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c77dfeb2-9115-47bf-878e-8ddbaf4c2c2d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnited%20joins%20an%20international%20trend%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Relax%20Row%20is%20a%20first%20in%20the%20US%20market%2C%20United%20is%20far%20from%20the%20first%20airline%20globally%20to%20think%20up%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairplane-economy-class-seat-concept-with-lie-flat-bed-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebed%20in%20economy%20class%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAir%20New%20Zealand%20patented%20the%20revolutionary%20Skycouch%20in%202011.%20Its%20version%20can%20cost%20from%20a%20few%20hundred%20dollars%20to%20over%20%241%2C500%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20nu