OpenAI%20pivots%20from%20a%20broad%20focus%20to%20prioritize%20key%20projects%2C%20shelving%20the%20Sora%20AI%20video%20app.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECEO%20of%20Applications%2C%20Fidji%20Simo%2C%20is%20pushing%20OpenAI%20to%20focus%20more.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESurging%20AI%20compute%20demand%20is%20forcing%20OpenAI%20to%20prioritize%20revenue-generating%20projects%20like%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Fidji%20Simo%20laid%20out%20a%20sharper%20strategy%20for%20OpenAI%3A%20the%20startup's%20everything%20era%20is%20over.%20Now%2C%20it's%20about%20focus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20cannot%20miss%20this%20moment%20because%20we%20are%20distracted%20by%20side%20quests%2C%26quot%3B%20Simo%20said%20at%20an%20all-hands%20meeting%2C%20according%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20must-read%20profile%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffidji-simo-openai-product-research-profitability-profile-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI's%20new%20CEO%20of%20applications%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20first%20%26quot%3Bside%20quests%26quot%3B%20to%20go%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-youtube-videos-ai-model-training-data-google-blocks-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESora%20AI%20video-generation%20app%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20product%20was%20a%20breakout%20hit%20when%20it%20launched%20last%20year.%20So%20why%20shut%20it%20down%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%20comes%20down%20to%20a%20growing%20constraint%20across%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-compute-compensation-software-engineers-greg-brockman-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20industry%3A%20compute%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221229%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22AI%20token%20use%20on%20Openrouter's%20model%20platform%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c31d4358b5806618e7e0c0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22528%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAI%20token%20use%20on%20Openrouter's%20model%20platform%3Cp%3EOpenRouter%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGiven%20the%20frantic%20search%20for%20more%20compute%20across%20the%20industry%2C%20OpenAI%20is%20prioritizing%20its%20greatest%20growth%20engine%20%E2%80%94%20ChatGPT%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ai-spending-boom-amazon-microsoft-google-will-play-out-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBernard%20Golden%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20CEO%20of%20Navica%2C%20a%20Silicon%20Valley-based%20tech%20analysis%2C%20consulting%2C%20and%20investment%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDemand%20for%20AI%20compute%20has%20surged%20in%20recent%20months.%20Data%20from%20OpenRouter's%20model%20platform%20shows%20usage%20more%20than%20tripled%20in%202.5%20months%2C%20a%20sign%20of%20explosive%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20supply%20isn't%20keeping%20up.%20Building%20new%20data%20centers%20has%20become%20harder%20due%20to%20local%20opposition%2C%20energy%20constraints%2C%20and%20shortages%20of%20key%20components%20such%20as%20memory%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20has%20moved%20aggressively%20to%20secure%20capacity%2C%20committing%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20to%20data%20center%20and%20chip%20deals.%20Even%20so%2C%20it%20still%20doesn't%20have%20enough%20compute%20to%20support%20everything%20it's%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20hinted%20at%20this%20reality%20in%20a%20statement%20confirming%20the%20Sora%20shutdown%3A%20%26quot%3BAs%20we%20focus%20and%20compute%20demand%20grows%2C%20the%20Sora%20research%20team%20continues%20to%20focus%20on%20world%20simulation%20research%20to%20advance%20robotics%20that%20will%20help%20people%20solve%20real-world%2C%20physical%20tasks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20day%2C%20OpenAI%20must%20decide%20which%20projects%20get%20access%20to%20scarce%20compute%20resources.%20That%20dynamic%20isn't%20unique%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20playing%20out%20across%20Silicon%20Valley.%20Before%20the%20latest%20surge%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-message-from-silicon-valley-no-one-slowing-down-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20CFO%20Sarah%20Friar%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehad%20spoken%20about%20these%20tradeoffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimo's%20background%20suggests%20how%20she'll%20approach%20this%20challenge.%20At%20Instacart%2C%20she%20used%20advertising%20to%20drive%20profitability%20and%20take%20the%20company%20public.%20Before%20that%2C%20she%20helped%20Facebook%20build%20a%20mobile%20ads%20business%20during%20a%20critical%20transition%20period%20leading%20up%20to%20its%20IPO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20she%20faces%20a%20similar%20situation%20at%20OpenAI.%20An%20IPO%20is%20expected%20within%20the%20next%20year%20or%20two%2C%20and%20the%20company%20is%20still%20losing%20billions%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20puts%20pressure%20on%20identifying%20projects%20that%20consume%20large%20amounts%20of%20compute%20without%20generating%20revenue.%20After%20years%20of%20experimentation%2C%20OpenAI%20has%20plenty%20of%20those.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESora%20is%20a%20prime%20example.%20The%20app%20allowed%20users%20to%20create%20AI-generated%20videos%2C%20an%20impressive%20and%20widely%20used%20tool.%20It%20didn't%20make%20money%2C%20and%20video%20generation%20is%20among%20the%20most%20compute-intensive%20AI%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20quite%20amazed%20by%20how%20much%20our%20power%20users%20want%20to%20use%20Sora%2C%20and%20the%20economics%20are%20currently%20completely%20unsustainable%2C%26quot%3B%20Bill%20Peebles%2C%20the%20head%20of%20Sora%2C%20wrote%20on%20X%20at%20the%20end%20of%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShutting%20down%20the%20Sora%20app%20will%20free%20up%20significant%20compute%20resources.%20OpenAI%20can%20now%20redirect%20that%20capacity%20toward%20products%20with%20clearer%20revenue%20potential%2C%20such%20as%20enterprise%20offerings%20like%20Codex%20or%20advertising%20within%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20environment%20defined%20by%20scarcity%2C%20focus%20is%20more%20important%20than%20ever%2C%20especially%20for%20a%20company%20like%20OpenAI%20that's%20losing%20so%20much%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESign%20up%20for%20BI's%20Tech%20Memo%20newsletter%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Ftech-memo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Reach%20out%20to%20me%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabarr%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabarr%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-kills-sora-app-ai-compute-crunch-forces-hard-choices-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774398231000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c320725b58f1f0f9336d95%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-kills-sora-app-ai-compute-crunch-forces-hard-choices-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22OpenAI's%20Fidji%20Simo%20focuses%20on%20profitability%2C%20shutting%20down%20Sora%20AI%20video%20app%20due%20to%20compute%20constraints%20in%20favor%20of%20ChatGPT's%20growth.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abarr%40businessinsider.com%20(Alistair%20Barr)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-kills-sora-app-ai-compute-crunch-forces-hard-choices-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lily%20Allen%2C%20Sam%20Fender%2C%20Max%20Richter%20and%20Ludovico%20Einaudi%20Revealed%20as%20First%20Honorees%20of%202026%20O2%20Silver%20Clef%20Awards%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A