onto%20Reels%20in%20the%20app.%3Cp%3EMeta%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMeta%20announced%20a%20slew%20of%20new%20shopping%20and%20advertising%20features%20to%20woo%20brands%20and%20creators.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20tech%20giant%20is%20bringing%20more%20affiliate%20marketing%20tools%20to%20both%20Facebook%20and%20Instagram.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20also%20rolling%20out%20AI-powered%20tools%20for%20brands.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMeta%20is%20diving%3C%2Fa%3E%20headfirst%20back%20into%20social%20shopping%20%E2%80%94%20with%20an%20AI%20twist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tech%20giant%20announced%20a%20slew%20of%20new%20shopping-related%20updates%20on%20Tuesday%20at%20the%20e-commerce%20conference%20Shoptalk%2C%20including%20affiliate%20marketing%20tools%20and%20AI-powered%20product%20recommendations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECreators%20are%20a%20core%20part%20of%20Meta's%20rollout.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20quick%20rundown%20of%20the%20shopping%20features%20Meta%20is%20pushing%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-money-with-affiliate-marketing%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAffiliate%20marketing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20is%20back.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Instagram%20creators%20can%20earn%20a%20commission%20from%20products%20tagged%20on%20reels%2C%20while%20Facebook%20creators%20will%20be%20able%20to%20earn%20from%20products%20tagged%20on%20reels%20and%20photos.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EGet%20ready%20for%20more%20detailed%20product%20descriptions%20on%20Facebook%20and%20Instagram%2C%20thanks%20to%20AI.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Meta%20is%20trying%20to%20make%20shopping%20a%20little%20easier%20for%20consumers%20by%20using%20AI%20to%20surface%20more%20information%2C%20such%20as%20reviews%20or%20product%20details%2C%20if%20a%20user%20clicks%20on%20an%20ad.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EChecking%20out%20is%20getting%20a%20makeover%2C%20too.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Facebook%20is%20rolling%20out%20a%20new%2C%20streamlined%20way%20to%20purchase%20items%20from%20ads%20with%20a%20one-click%20%26quot%3Bbuy%20now%26quot%3B%20button.%20Advertisers%20can%20select%20a%20checkout%20partner%20such%20as%20PayPal%20or%20Stripe.%20Some%20early%20businesses%20enrolled%20in%20this%20experience%20include%201-800-Flowers%2C%20Fanatics%2C%20and%20Quince.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdvertisers%20can%20get%20more%20granular.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Meta%20is%20allowing%20advertisers%2C%20specifically%20retail%20media%20networks%20(like%20Target%2C%20Walmart%2C%20or%20Amazon)%2C%20to%20choose%20specific%20products%20from%20their%20catalogs%20instead%20of%20running%20broader%20campaigns.%20Brands%20can%20also%20leverage%20Meta's%20AI%20to%20recommend%20what%20content%20format%20the%20product%20appears%20in%2C%20such%20as%20a%20story%2C%20reel%2C%20or%20carousel.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMeta's%20pitch%20to%20brands%20and%20advertisers%20is%20that%20these%20tools%20will%20not%20just%20drive%20awareness%2C%20but%20also%20more%20clicks%20and%20purchases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20reported%20that%20its%20ad%20impressions%20increased%2018%25%20year%20over%20year%20in%20the%20fourth%20quarter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220a8fd79a-bcb5-40ca-9705-c8da118b0055%5C%22%3EReturn%20of%20the%20affiliate%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20affiliate%20experiences%20differ%20slightly%20between%20the%20two%20Meta%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Instagram%2C%20creators%20can%20add%20products%20directly%20from%20Meta's%20brand%20catalog%20to%20their%20reels.%20Influencers%20can%20also%20add%20outside%20URLs%2C%20such%20as%20third-party%20affiliate%20links%20from%20brands%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finfluencer-app-ltk-takes-step-ai-shopping-new-chatbot-chatgpt-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eplatforms%20like%20LTK%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20ShopMy%2C%20but%20only%20if%20the%20product%20is%20in%20Meta's%20catalog%20already.%20Creators%20are%20capped%20at%2030%20products%20per%20reel%2C%20and%20any%20link%20must%20point%20to%20a%20single%20product%2C%20not%20a%20collection.%20Eligible%20creators%20%E2%80%94%20who%20must%20be%20at%20least%2018%20years%20old%20and%20have%20at%20least%201%2C000%20followers%20%E2%80%94%20will%20soon%20see%20an%20%26quot%3Badd%20products%26quot%3B%20option%20in%20their%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20creators%20could%20direct%20their%20followers%20to%20affiliate%20links%20on%20Instagram%20via%20links%20in%20bio%2C%20DMs%2C%20or%20stories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20on%20Facebook%2C%20creators%20can%20include%20shoppable%20links%20to%20their%20reels%20or%20photo%20posts%20and%20earn%20a%20commission.%20Facebook's%20%26quot%3Baffiliate%20partnerships%26quot%3B%20program%20will%20launch%20in%20partnership%20with%20two%20major%20retailers%2C%20Amazon%20for%20US%20creators%20and%20Shopee%20for%20creators%20in%20select%20Asian%20markets.%20Facebook%20teased%20that%20it%20would%20add%20more%20partners%2C%20including%20Mercado%20Libre%2C%20Temu%2C%20and%20eBay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECommission%20rates%20are%20set%20by%20the%20brand%20partners%20for%20both%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20Meta's%20first%20rodeo%20with%20a%20native%20affiliate%20marketing%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstagram-ending-influencer-affiliate-program-test-focus-creator-brand-marketplace-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EInstagram%20sunset%20a%20test%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20allowed%20some%20influencers%20to%20earn%20a%20commission%20on%20products%20tagged%20in%20their%20posts.%20The%20beta%20program%20lasted%20about%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20Meta%20caused%20a%20stir%20among%20influencers%20after%20an%20AI-powered%20%26quot%3BShop%20the%20Look%26quot%3B%20feature%20popped%20up%20on%20some%20creators'%20content%2C%20but%20di