C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eand%20Paramount%2B%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20are%20also%20exploring%20short-form%20clips.%20All%20these%20services%20are%20looking%20for%20ways%20to%20juice%20engagement%2C%20particularly%20on%20mobile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20losing%20Sora%20is%20a%20blow%20to%20Disney's%20strategy.%20D'Amaro%20told%20employees%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-ceo-josh-damaro-first-day-memo-employees-walden-iger-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ein%20his%20introductory%20memo%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20week%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20prioritize%20%26quot%3Bimmersive%2C%20interactive%2C%20and%20personal%20ways%20for%20people%20to%20experience%20Disney.%26quot%3B%20Analysts%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjosh-damaro-disney-priorities-video-games-ai-espn-tv-networks-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehighlighted%20interactive%20elements%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20like%20AI%2C%20as%20a%20way%20for%20Disney%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-streaming-engagement-viewership-growth-hulu-integration-ai-generated-video-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eboost%20streaming%20engagement%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Disney%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20they%20%26quot%3Brespect%20OpenAI's%20decision%20to%20exit%20the%20video%20generation%20business%20and%20to%20shift%20its%20priorities%20elsewhere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20appreciate%20the%20constructive%20collaboration%20between%20our%20teams%20and%20what%20we%20learned%20from%20it%2C%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20engage%20with%20AI%20platforms%20to%20find%20new%20ways%20to%20meet%20fans%20where%20they%20are%20while%20responsibly%20embracing%20new%20technologies%20that%20respect%20IP%20and%20the%20rights%20of%20creators%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Disney%20spokesperson%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fdb6c3b1-ef61-4196-9d4a-6e2671e25c1c%5C%22%3EGetting%20engagement%20after%20the%20OpenAI%20marriage%20unravels%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWithout%20OpenAI's%20help%2C%20D'Amaro%20will%20need%20other%20ways%20to%20make%20Disney's%20flagship%20streaming%20service%20more%20engaging%2C%20especially%20for%20younger%20audiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDisney's%20streamers%2C%20led%20by%20Disney%2B%20and%20Hulu%2C%20accounted%20for%20a%204.9%25%20viewership%20share%20on%20US%20TVs%20in%20January%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nielsen.com%2Fdata-center%2Fthe-gauge%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Nielsen%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That's%20only%20marginally%20higher%20than%20the%204.4%25%20combined%20share%20that%20those%20two%20streamers%20had%20in%20May%202021%20%E2%80%94%20nearly%20five%20years%20ago.%20And%20it's%20well%20below%20Disney%2B%20and%20Hulu's%20peak%20viewership%20share%20in%20July%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FIeFL5%2F5%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Disney%20streaming%20viewership%20share%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22394%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EDisney%20isn't%20alone%2C%20as%20its%20paid%20streaming%20peers%20have%20struggled%20to%20keep%20pace%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutube-free-streamers-streaming-inflation-disney-hbo-max-netflix-hollywood-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eexplosive%20growth%20of%20free%20streamers%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20YouTube%2C%20whose%20US%20viewership%20share%20has%20more%20than%20doubled%20from%206%25%20to%2012.5%25%20from%20May%202021%20to%20January%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsumers%20have%20flocked%20toward%20free%20services%20as%20paid%20streamers%2C%20including%20Disney%2B%20and%20Hulu%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-plus-price-increase-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econsistently%20raise%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYouTube%20may%20also%20be%20winning%20viewers%20for%20other%20reasons%2C%20such%20as%20its%20interactive%20comment%20sections%20and%20the%20emotional%20connections%20fans%20have%20with%20their%20favorite%20creators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWill%20Disney%20find%20another%20AI%20partner%20to%20dance%20with%3F%20That's%20a%20call%20D'Amaro%20must%20now%20make.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-openai-deal-breakup-test-ceo-josh-damaro-short-form-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774392250000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c2fd565b58f1f0f9336cc8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-openai-deal-breakup-test-ceo-josh-damaro-short-form-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22OpenAI%20and%20Disney's%20deal%20is%20ending.%20New%20CEO%20Josh%20D'Amaro%20will%20need%20to%20find%20other%20ways%20to%20boost%20streaming%20engagement.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jfaris%40businessinsider.com%20(James%20Faris)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-openai-deal-breakup-test-ceo-josh-damaro-short-form-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meta%20Ordered%20To%20Pay%20%24375%20Million%20Over%20Child%20Exploitation%2C%20User%20Safety%20Claims%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22A%20New%20Mexico%20jury%20on%20Tuesday%20found%20social%20media%20giant%20Meta%20liable%20for%20endangering%20children%20by%20making%20them%20vulnerable%20to%20predators%20on%20its%20platforms%20and%20other%20dangers.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774392228000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Ffvnvpaig_mark-zuckerberg-_625x300_17_April_25.jpeg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmeta-ordered-to-pay-375-million-over-child-exploitation-user-safety-claims-11262371%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20New%20Mexico%20jury%20on%20Tuesday%20found%20social%20media%20giant%20Meta%20liable%20for%20endangering%20children%20by%20making%20them%20vulnerable%20to%20predators%20on%20its%20platforms%20and%20other%20dangers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmeta-ordered-to-pay-375-million-over-child-exploitation-user-safety-claims-11262371%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmeta-ordered-to-pay-375-million-over-child-exploitation-user-safety-claims-11262371%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmeta-ordered-to-pay-375-million-over-child-exploitation-user-safety-claims-11262371%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20went%20to%20LaGuardia.%20The%20security%20line%20looped%20around%20the%20terminal%20four%20times.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20lines%20at%20TSA%20and%20a%20selfie%20from%20BI%20reporter%20Henry%20Chandonnet.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c341ad58b5806618e7e136%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20lines%20were%20long%20at%20LaGuardia.%3Cp%3EHenry%20Chandonnet%3B%20CHARLY%20TRIBALLEAU%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20siblings%20had%20come%20to%20New%20York%20for%20their%20father's%20funeral.%20They%20then%20found%20themselves%20stuck%20at%20the%20city's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fair-canada-plane-collision-laguardia-airport-shut-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELaGuardia%20Airport%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrincess%20Ivie%2C%20a%20nursing%20student%20in%20Texas%2C%20and%20her%20brother%2C%20Prince%20Eweka%2C%20were%20sitting%20in%20the%20baggage%20drop-off%20zone%20Tuesday%20morning%2C%20waiting%20to%20reschedule%20their%20flights.%20Ivie%20had%20slept%20through%20the%20notification%20that%20her%20flight%20had%20been%20moved%20up%20by%204%20hours%2C%20to%206%20a.m.%20Eweka%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Ohio%20and%20works%20in%20a%20restaurant%2C%20had%20also%20missed%20his%20flight%20%E2%80%94%20in%20his%20case%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20long%20security%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20a%20two-and-a-half-hour%20wait%20on%20the%20line.%20By%20the%20time%20I%20got%20halfway%20through%2C%20I%20had%20already%20missed%20my%20flight%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairport-lounge-vs-bar-travel-flying-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eairports%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20the%20country%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsa-wait-times-airports-with-longest-delays-how-to-check-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etravelers%20are%20facing%20hourslong%20security%20lines%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20stretching%20into%20parking%20garages%2C%20as%20a%20five-week%20government%20shutdown%20leaves%20around%2047%2C000%20TSA%20agents%20unpaid%20and%20many%20off%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20disruption%20deepened%20Sunday%20night%2C%20when%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faudio-captures-final-moments-before-plane-truck-collision-at-laguardia-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAir%20Canada%20plane%20collided%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20firetruck%20while%20landing%20at%20LaGuardia%2C%20killing%20two%20pilots%20and%20forcing%20one%20of%20the%20nation's%20busiest%20airports%20to%20shut%20down%20for%20hours%2C%20delaying%20or%20canceling%20hundreds%20of%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20to%20LaGuardia's%20Terminal%20B%20on%20Tuesday%20morning%20to%20get%20a%20sense%20of%20what%20travelers%20were%20up%20against.%20The%20security%20line%20looped%20around%20the%20terminal%20four%20times.%20By%20mid-morning%2C%20an%20agent%20told%20me%20it%20would%20take%2090%20minutes%20to%20reach%20the%20front%20of%20the%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20late%20Tuesday%2C%20there%20was%20some%20optimism%20that%20a%20deal%20could%20be%20reached%20to%20end%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-government-partial-shutdown-minnesota-homeland-security-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epartial%20government%20shutdown%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20restore%20the%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security's%20funding.%20Congress%20is%20due%20to%20begin%20a%20two-week%20recess%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EMultiple%20travelers%20told%20me%20they'd%20been%20stuck%20in%20limbo%20for%20days.%20There%20was%20a%20sense%20that%20traveling%20%E2%80%94%20never%20easy%20%E2%80%94%20shouldn't%20be%20this%20hard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20Departures%20Hall%20was%20full%20of%20people%20trying%20to%20make%20the%20most%20of%20a%20bad%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe'll%20laugh%20about%20it%20someday%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Pam%20Collins.%20She%20had%20just%20learned%20that%20her%20flight%20back%20home%20to%20Nashville%20had%20been%20canceled%2C%20and%20she%20was%20waiting%20to%20check%20in%20to%20her%20hotel.%20Her%20New%20York%20vacation%20had%20been%20a%20blast%20%E2%80%94%20a%20walk%20through%20Central%20Park%2C%20a%20great%20meal%20in%20Chinatown%20%E2%80%94%20but%20she%20was%20ready%20to%20be%20home.%20She%20missed%20her%20dog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERuth%20Garcia%2C%20who%20was%20visiting%20from%20El%20Paso%2C%20was%20sitting%20on%20a%20bench%2C%20resting%20her%20feet%20while%20her%20husband%20held%20her%20spot%20in%20the%20TSA%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%20to%20her%20was%20Cindy%20Willard%2C%20who%20was%20expecting%20to%20still%20be%20at%20LaGuardia%20when%20Garcia%20landed%20back%20in%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWillard's%20Sunday%20night%20flight%20to%20Nashville%20had%20been%20canceled%20when%20the%20airport%20shut%20down%2C%20and%20she%20arrived%20at%205%3A30%20in%20the%20morning%20for%20a%20rescheduled%20flight.%20That%20flight%2C%20and%20then%20another%2C%20had%20been%20canceled.%20She%20was%20hoping%20to%20get%20on%20another%20late-night%20flight%2C%20but%20the%20airline%20told%20her%20she'd%20have%20to%20wait%20to%20drop%20off%20her%20bags.%20So%20she%20was%20camped%20out%20on%20a%20bench%20with%20her%20suitcases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENearby%2C%20a%20group%20of%2020%20high%20school%20students%20from%20Boise%2C%20Idaho%2C%20had%20arranged%20themselves%20in%20small%20groups%20and%20were%20playing%20cards.%20They%20were%20part%20of%20a%20200-member%20choir%20trip%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20were%20gradually%20flying%20home%20in%20groups%20after%20their%20original%20flight%20was%20canceled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20they%20were%20among%20the%20last%20from%20their%20group%20to%20leave%2C%20they'd%20had%20an%20extra%20day%20to%20explore%20Times%20Square%2C%20and%20a%20few%20of%20them%20went%20to%20a%20hockey%20game.%20But%20their%20initial%20excitement%20had%20faded%20to%20frustration%20and%20boredom.%20%26quot%3BSome%20of%20these%20kids%20are%20just%20really%20ready%20to%20go%20home%20and%20see%20their%20parents%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Melanie%20Nelson%2C%20one%20of%20their%20chaperones.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20teenagers%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20feelings.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20people%20wandered%20over%20from%20the%20arrivals%20terminal%20to%20upstairs%20to%20marvel%20at%20the%20state%20of%20the%20security%20lines%20and%20get%20a%20sense%20of%20what%20they%20were%20in%20for%20at%20the%20end%20of%20their%20trips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20be%20super%20early%20when%20we%20fly%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Angela%20Bruccoli%2C%20who%20had%20traveled%20with%20her%20daughter%2C%20Ashley%2C%20from%20South%20Carolina%20to%20celebrate%20Ashley's%2021st%20birthday.%20She%20was%20trying%20not%20to%20get%20upset%20about%20the%20long%20line%20because%20she%20had%20no%20control%20over%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMary%20Bruccoli%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20New%20York%2C%20chimed%20in%20with%20her%20rendition%20of%20%26quot%3BLet%20go%2C%20let%20God%26quot%3B%3A%20%26quot%3BLet%20go%2C%20let%20TSA.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStaring%20down%20the%20long%20line%20in%20front%20of%20me%2C%20I%20worried%20about%20my%20future%20travel.%20I%20have%20a%20trip%20to%20Amsterdam%20booked%20in%20just%20a%20few%20weeks.%20Will%20the%20shutdown%20end%3F%20Will%20the%20lines%20abate%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20I%20got%20a%20ping%20from%20a%20colleague%2C%20who'd%20just%20arrived%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20security%20line.%20He'd%20made%20it%20through%20in%20just%20under%20an%20hour.%20It%20seemed%20like%20a%20good%20sign.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fhenry-chandonnet%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHenry%20Chandonnet%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20reporter%20on%20the%20Business%20News%20desk%20at%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravelers-airport-chaos-laguardia-tsa-shutdown-travel-flying-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774392214000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c310cae98a37a4841f3476%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravelers-airport-chaos-laguardia-tsa-shutdown-travel-flying-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20government%20shutdown%20is%20snarling%20airports%20nationwide%20%E2%80%94%20here's%20what%20it%20looks%20like%20on%20the%20ground%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hchandonnet%40insider.com%20(Henry%20Chandonnet)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravelers-airport-chaos-laguardi