%20deposition%20is%20played%20for%20the%20jurors%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20March%204%2C%202026%2C%20in%20Santa%20Fe%2C%20N.M.%20(Jim%20Weber%2FSanta%20Fe%20New%20Mexican%20via%20AP%2C%20Pool)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c2a09958b5806618e7dc72%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222045%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELawyers%20for%20the%20plaintiff%20watch%20on%20a%20laptop%20as%20a%20recording%20of%20Meta%20Founder%20and%20CEO%20Mark%20Zuckerberg's%20deposition%20is%20played%20for%20the%20jurors%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20March%204%2C%202026%2C%20in%20Santa%20Fe%2C%20N.M.%3Cp%3EJim%20Weber%2FSanta%20Fe%20New%20Mexican%20via%20AP%2C%20Pool%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20New%20Mexico%20jury%20found%20Meta%20liable%20for%20failing%20to%20protect%20kids%20from%20sexual%20exploitation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20jury%20approved%20a%20%24375%20million%20fine%20for%20Meta.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMeta%20said%20it%20disagrees%20with%20the%20verdict%20and%20will%20be%20filing%20appeals.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20shaping%20up%20to%20be%20a%20big%20month%20of%20verdicts%20for%20Meta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20jurors%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20deliberate%20over%20Meta%20and%20Google's%20liability%20in%20a%20case%20about%20social%20media%20addiction%2C%20in%20New%20Mexico%2C%20Meta%20was%20found%20liable%20in%20a%20separate%20case%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkids-parenting-social-media-bans-meta-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echild%20safety%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20its%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNew%20Mexico%20is%20proud%20to%20be%20the%20first%20state%20to%20hold%20Meta%20accountable%20in%20court%20for%20misleading%20parents%2C%20enabling%20child%20exploitation%2C%20and%20harming%20kids%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20New%20Mexico%20Attorney%20General%20Ra%C3%BAl%20Torrez%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20court%2C%20the%20state%20proposed%20to%20the%20jury%20penalties%20of%20up%20to%20roughly%20%242.2%20billion%20in%20fines.%20The%20jury%2C%20however%2C%20awarded%20the%20lesser%20amount%20of%20%24375%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20next%20phase%20of%20this%20legal%20proceeding%2C%20we%20will%20seek%20additional%20financial%20penalties%20and%20court-mandated%20changes%20to%20Meta's%20platforms%20that%20offer%20stronger%20protections%20for%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20Torrez%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20respectfully%20disagree%20with%20the%20verdict%20and%20will%20appeal.%20We%20work%20hard%20to%20keep%20people%20safe%20on%20our%20platforms%20and%20are%20clear%20about%20the%20challenges%20of%20identifying%20and%20removing%20bad%20actors%20or%20harmful%20content%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Meta%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20continue%20to%20defend%20ourselves%20vigorously%2C%20and%20we%20remain%20confident%20in%20our%20record%20of%20protecting%20teens%20online%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-legal-battle-ai-chatbot-records-child-safety-case-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENew%20Mexico%20lawsuit%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20brought%20by%20Torrez%20in%202023%2C%20accused%20Meta%20of%20violating%20the%20state's%20Unfair%20Trade%20Practices%20Act.%20New%20Mexico's%20DOJ%20argued%20in%20court%20that%20Meta%20prioritized%20profits%20over%20protecting%20children%20on%20its%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20the%20course%20of%20a%20decade%2C%20Meta%20has%20failed%20over%20and%20over%20again%20to%20act%20honestly%20and%20transparently%2C%26quot%3B%20Linda%20Singer%2C%20the%20state%20attorney%2C%20told%20the%20jury%20during%20the%20trial's%20closing%20arguments%20on%20Monday.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20failed%20to%20act%20to%20protect%20young%20people%20in%20this%20state.%20It%20is%20up%20to%20you%20to%20finish%20this%20job.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20clear%20that%20young%20people%20are%20spending%20too%20much%20time%20on%20Meta's%20products%3B%20they've%20lost%20control%2C%26quot%3B%20Singer%20added.%20%26quot%3BMeta%20knew%20that%2C%20and%20it%20didn't%20disclose%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESinger%20also%20said%20in%20her%20closing%20statement%20said%20that%20the%20company%20failed%20to%20enforce%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-millions-underage-users-open-secret-states-say-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eminimum%20user%20age%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%2013%2C%20and%20that%20testimonies%20showed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-community-notes-elon-musk-x-algorithm-facebook-instagram-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMeta's%20algorithms%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20been%20recommending%20sensational%20and%20harmful%20content%20to%20teenagers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20pointed%20to%20its%20policies%2C%20including%20the%20introduction%20of%20Teen%20Accounts%20and%20additional%20parental%20control%20tools.%20Based%20on%20Meta's%20user%20policy%20webpage%2C%20Meta%20has%20had%20a%20minimum%20age%20requirement%20of%20%3Cmark%20data-color%3D%5C%22rgba(0%2C%200%2C%200%2C%200)%5C%22%3E13%20years%20old%20for%20Facebook%20and%20Instagram%20since%202006.%3C%2Fmark%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-found-liable-new-mexico-suit-protect-children-sexual-exploitation-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774390534000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c2a0a758b5806618e7dc75%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-found-liable-new-mexico-suit-protect-children-sexual-exploitation-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20jury%20in%20New%20Mexico%20found%20Meta%20liable%20for%20failing%20to%20protect%20kids%20from%20sexual%20exploitation%20