Latin%20dancing%20dramedy%20%E2%80%98Chacach%C3%A1!%E2%80%99%20won%20big%20Tuesday%20night%20at%20France%E2%80%99s%20Series%20Mania%2C%20Europe%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20TV%20festival%2C%20scooping%20the%20prizes%20offered%20by%20its%20three%20biggest%20industry%20events%2C%20the%20Series%20Mania%20Forum%E2%80%99s%20Buyers%20Upfront%20and%20Co-Pro%20Pitching%20Sessions%20and%20SeriesMakers.%C2%A0%20All%20suggest%20a%20broader%20audience%20ambition%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22John%20Hopewell%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kevin%20DiCicco%2C%20Creator%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Air%20Bud%E2%80%99%20Character%2C%20Dies%20at%2063%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774390131000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236698445%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kevin%20DiCicco%2C%20the%20dog%20trainer%20and%20creator%20behind%20the%20beloved%20%E2%80%9CAir%20Bud%E2%80%9D%20film%20franchise%2C%20has%20died%20at%20the%20age%20of%2063%2C%20his%20family%20confirmed.%20DiCicco%20died%20March%2021%20in%20San%20Diego%20after%20spending%20time%20in%20hospice%20care%2C%20his%20brother%20Mark%20told%20TMZ.%20DiCicco%20first%20rose%20to%20national%20attention%20when%20he%20rescued%20a%20stray%20Golden%20Retriever%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Kennedy%20French%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20runway%20safety%20alert%20didn't%20notify%20ATC%20of%20a%20potential%20collision%20before%20the%20deadly%20Air%20Canada%20crash%2C%20the%20NTSB%20head%20said%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224096%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22NTSB%20investigators%20at%20the%20scene%20of%20the%20Air%20Canada%20crash.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c307afe98a37a4841f3438%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENTSB%20investigators%20found%20that%20a%20safety%20system%20designed%20to%20alert%20ATC%20of%20impending%20runway%20collisions%20didn't%20activate%20before%20the%20Air%20Canada%20crash.%3Cp%3ENTSB%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20NTSB%20said%20the%20truck%20that%20collided%20with%20a%20regional%20jet%20in%20New%20York%20didn't%20have%20a%20transponder.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20said%20the%20lack%20of%20equipment%20prevented%20a%20runway%20warning%20system%20called%20ASDE-X%20from%20activating.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EASDE-X%20uses%20radar%20and%20satellite%20data%20to%20track%20ground%20movements%20and%20alert%20ATC%20of%20potential%20conflicts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20head%20of%20the%20National%20Transportation%20Safety%20Board%20said%20a%20critical%20alert%20designed%20to%20prevent%20runway%20collisions%20didn't%20trigger%20before%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fair-canada-plane-collision-laguardia-airport-shut-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edeadly%20Air%20Canada%20crash%3C%2Fa%3E%20Sunday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Airport%20Surface%20Detection%20Equipment%2C%20Model%20X%2C%20rolled%20out%20between%202003%20and%202011%2C%20is%20a%20ground%20surveillance%20system%20that%20uses%20radar%20and%20satellite%20data%20to%20track%20aircraft%20and%20vehicles%20and%20alert%20air%20traffic%20control%20of%20potential%20conflicts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20deployed%20at%2035%20major%20airports%20across%20the%20US%2C%20including%20LaGuardia%20in%20New%20York%2C%20where%20a%20regional%20Bombardier%20CRJ-900%20jet%20operated%20by%20Jazz%20Aviation%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fntsb-updates-air-canada-crash-says-tsa-lines-delayed-investigator-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAir%20Canada%20Express%20collided%20with%20a%20fire%20truck%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%2011%20p.m.%20Sunday%2C%20killing%20two%20pilots%20and%20hospitalizing%2041%20others%2C%20though%20many%20have%20been%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENTSB%20Chair%20Jennifer%20Homendy%20said%20this%20system%2C%20known%20as%20ASDE-X%2C%20however%2C%20didn't%20activate%20that%20night%20%26quot%3Bdue%20to%20the%20close%20proximity%20of%20vehicles%20merging%20and%20unmerging%20near%20the%20runway%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20inability%20to%20create%20a%20track%20of%20high%20confidence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20later%20said%20that%20the%20fire%20truck's%20lack%20of%20a%20transponder%20contributed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20order%20for%20ASDE-X%20to%20work%2C%20well%2C%20you%20have%20to%20know%20where%20ground%20vehicles%20and%20aircraft%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20that%20ground%20vehicle%20did%20not%20have%20a%20transponder.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20truck%20without%20a%20transponder%20might%20appear%20on%20ASDE%E2%80%91X%20radar%2C%20but%20it%20may%20not%20trigger%20the%20system's%20automatic%20alert%20that's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdc-plane-crash-aviation-experts-long-feared-nightmare-scenario-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edesigned%20to%20notify%20the%20controller%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20FAA%20slide%20showing%20ASDE-X.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c308ef5b58f1f0f9336d31%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22721%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20FAA%20slide%20showing%20how%20ASDE-X%20works%3A%20multiple%20sensors%20feed%20aircraft%20and%20vehicle%20data%20to%20a%20display%20in%20the%20air%20traffic%20control%20tower.%3Cp%3EFederal%20Aviation%20Administration%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EVideos%20shared%20online%20show%20several%20emergency%20vehicles%20holding%20short%20of%20Runway%204%2C%20where%20the%20collision%20occurred%2C%20and%20one%20truck%20moving%20forward.%20The%20truck%20had%20been%20responding%20to%20a%20separate%20plane%20on%20the%20airfield%20with%20an%20odor%20issue%20and%20received%20clearance%20to%20cross%20the%20runway%20less%20than%20a%20minute%20before%20the%20CRJ%20touched%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faudio-captures-final-moments-before-plane-truck-collision-at-laguardia-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAudio%20tapes%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20ATC%20Live%20reveal%20the%20controller%20repeatedly%20told%20the%20truck%20to%20%26quot%3Bstop%26quot%3B%20before%20the%20crash.%20It's%20unknown%20why%20the%20driver%2C%20who%20was%20reportedly%20injured%20but%20alive%2C%20didn't%20respond%20to%20the%20controller's%20instruction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHomendy%20said%20there%20is%20still%20a%20lot%20of%20data%20to%20collect%20and%20interviews%20to%20conduct%2C%20so%20it's%20impossible%20to%20say%20whether%20the%20ASDE-X%20system%20could%20have%20provided%20the%20controller%20enough%20time%20to%20react%20and%20prevent%20the%20crash.%20She%20added%20that%20there%20may%20be%20multiple%20root%20causes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20rarely%2C%20if%20ever%2C%20investigate%20a%20major%20accident%20where%20it%20was%20one%20failure%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famericans-fear-flying-aviation-safety-plane-crash-fears-faa-firings-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOur%20aviation%20system%20is%20incredibly%20safe%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20there%20are%20multiple%2C%20multiple%20layers%20of%20defense%20built%20in%20to%20prevent%20an%20accident%2C%20so%20when%20something%20goes%20wrong%2C%20that%20means%20many%2C%20many%20things%20went%20wrong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReliable%20warning%20and%20detection%20systems%20have%20long%20been%20a%20focus%20of%20the%20NTSB.%20The%20agency%20has%20called%20for%20improvements%20to%20ASDE-X%2C%20like%20sending%20the%20alert%20to%20pilots%2C%20not%20just%20controllers.%20It%20has%20also%20previously%20recommended%20expanding%20the%20safety%20technology%20to%20more%20airports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20similar%20lines%2C%20the%20NTSB%20recently%20recommended%20equipping%20certain%20military%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-improve-air-safety-following-american-crash-stalled-in-congress-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eaircraft%20with%20a%20detection%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20could%20display%20nearby%20traffic%20to%20pilots%20%E2%80%94%20technology%20that%20it%20said%20may%20have%20helped%20prevent%20the%20January%202025%20midair%20collision%20between%20an%20Army%20helicopter%20and%20an%20American%20Airlines%20regional%20jet%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20that%20killed%2067%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndustry%20analysts%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnear-miss-incidents-wakeup-call-to-the-aviation-industry-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewarning%20about%20runway%20collisions%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20years.%20In%202023%2C%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%20convened%20a%20panel%20to%20address%20several%20close%20calls%20at%20US%20airports.%20FAA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.faa.gov%2Fairports%2Frunway_safety%2Fstatistics%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata%3C%2Fa%3E%20shows%20that%201%2C760%20runway%20incursions%2C%20as%20these%20close%20calls%20and%20accidents%20are%20known%2C%20were%20reported%20in%20that%20fiscal%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20numbers%20were%201%2C758%20in%202024%20and%201%2C636%20in%202026.%20There%20have%20been%20about%20500%20reported%20so%20far%20in%202026%20%E2%80%94%20including%20a%20close%20call%20a%20week%20before%20the%20Air%20Canada%20crash%2C%20when%20an%20Alaska%20Airlines%20plane%20almost%20collided%20with%20a%20FedEx%20plane%20on%20crossing%20runways%20in%20nearby%20Newark%2C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20on%20March%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frunway-safety-alert-didnt-activate-before-deadly-air-canada-crash-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774389983000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c307afe98a37a4841f3438%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frunway-safety-alert-didnt-activate-before-deadly-air-canada-crash-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Investigators%20found%20that%20a%20safety%20system%20designed%20to%20alert%20air%20traffic%20control%20of%20impending%20collisions%20didn't%20activate%20before%20the%20Air%20Canada%20crash.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22trains%40businessinsider.com%20(Taylor%20Rains)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frunway-safety-alert-didnt-activate-before-deadly-air-canada-crash-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20is%20an%20email%20alias%2C%20and%20how%20does%20it%20protect%20your%20privacy%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20through%20our%20links%2C%20Business%20Insider%20may%20earn%20an%20affiliate%20commission.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fabout-us%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELearn%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20business%20person%20holds%20a%20shield%20up%20against%20spam%20and%20scam%20email%20icons%20rushing%20towards%20them%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c18c2758b5806618e7d870%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3Etommy%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEmail%20spam%20used%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20major%20annoyances%20of%20the%20digital%20world.%20But%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20email%20providers%20have%20taken%20steps%20to%20improve%20our%20overflowing%20inboxes%2C%20which%20were%20often%20riddled%20with%20distractions%20and