se%20are%20mainly%20about%20privacy.%20Instead%20of%20giving%20your%20real%20email%2C%20a%20completely%20random%20one%20will%20be%20generated%2C%20while%20still%20sending%20your%20email%20to%20your%20real%20inbox%2C%20as%20available%20with%20a%20service%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15118297617va-20%26h%3Dfc73eccc0c4e0fece21dc5e7e497a34a7930389a3307c24255f27e8dad7a78f8%26postID%3D69c189225ebd47b37dfd7714%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fwhat-is-an-email-alias%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fproton.me%252Fmail%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EProton%20Mail%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22704bbee4-58c8-48bf-90af-1f0fc7447fad%5C%22%3EHow%20email%20aliases%20can%20protect%20your%20privacy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20email%20aliases%20are%20simply%20helpful%20ways%20to%20organise%20your%20inbox%2C%20or%20effective%20tools%20for%20making%20it%20easier%20to%20contact%20your%20business.%20However%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20time%2C%20the%20main%20benefit%20is%20protecting%20your%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20done%20in%20a%20few%20ways%2C%20but%20mainly%20by%20reducing%20how%20much%20your%20email%20appears%20online.%20Of%20course%2C%20your%20aliases%20will%20still%20appear%20and%20can%20be%20used%2C%20but%20these%20can%20be%20deleted%20at%20any%20time.%20Your%20actual%20core%20email%20address%20becomes%20harder%20to%20find%20the%20more%20you%20use%20aliases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20more%20privacy%2C%20as%20it%20hides%20your%20main%20address%20from%20marketers%2C%20spam%2C%20and%20phishing%20attempts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20your%20data%20is%20used%2C%20it%20is%20also%20easier%20to%20identify%20who%20has%20misused%20it.%20If%20you%20give%20email%20aliases%20in%20certain%20situations%2C%20it%20is%20easier%20to%20track%20where%20they%20have%20been%20misused.%20As%20soon%20as%20you%20can%20tell%20someone%20is%20misusing%20an%20alias%2C%20you%20can%20delete%20it%20and%20start%20again%2C%20instead%20of%20being%20stuck%20with%20a%20boatload%20of%20spam%20and%20no%20clear%20way%20to%20tell%20how%20they%20have%20your%20email%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20useful%20as%20aliases%20can%20be%20for%20privacy%2C%20they%20aren't%20a%20surefire%20solution%20to%20keeping%20you%20safe%20online.%20They%20don't%20stop%20tracking%20cookies%2C%20and%20they%20don't%20automatically%20encrypt%20emails.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220538d647-4103-4ac6-818c-f6a4e5c2d9b2%5C%22%3ETypes%20of%20email%20aliases%20(and%20how%20they%20differ)%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20mentioned%20above%2C%20there%20are%20three%20main%20types%20of%20email%20aliases.%20Each%20one%20has%20a%20different%20purpose%2C%20but%20all%20three%20can%20be%20useful%20depending%20on%20your%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch4%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a8dfb424-6483-4b38-940e-26ef4ec863cd%5C%22%3EPlus%20addressing%20(yourname%2Blabel%40%E2%80%A6)%3C%2Fh4%3E%3Cp%3EThink%20of%20plus%20addressing%20as%20an%20organisational%20alias.%20It%20works%20by%20adding%20a%20%2B%20symbol%20to%20the%20end%20of%20the%20name%20part%20of%20your%20email%20before%20the%20%40%20symbol%2C%20along%20with%20a%20category.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20your%20email%20is%20testing%40gmail.com%2C%20you%20could%20add%20a%20%2B%20symbol%20to%20make%20it%20testing%2Bshopping%40gmail.com.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20type%20of%20email%20alias%2C%20you%20can%20use%20it%20as%20a%20category%20in%20different%20situations.%20A%20shopping%20%2B%20tag%20when%20you%20sign%20up%20for%20mailing%20lists%20from%20your%20favourite%20shops%2C%20one%20for%20subscriptions%2C%20and%20one%20for%20emails%20related%20to%20your%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20as%20an%20extra%20step%2C%20you%20can%20make%20rules%20within%20your%20email%20to%20file%20any%20email%20sent%20to%20these%20aliases%20into%20specific%20folders.%20This%20is%20less%20about%20privacy%20and%20more%20about%20keeping%20everything%20organised.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20top%20of%20that%2C%20this%20is%20a%20great%20way%20to%20know%20which%20of%20your%20aliases%20has%20been%20compromised%20if%20you%20start%20getting%20lots%20of%20spam%20or%20emails%20you%20don't%20want.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20is%20worth%20noting%20that%20some%20sites%20will%20block%20%2B%20label%20aliases%2C%20so%20they%20aren't%20always%20a%20sure-fire%20solution.%20Not%20to%20mention%2C%20there%20isn't%20really%20any%20privacy%20here%2C%20as%20it%20is%20still%20very%20clear%20what%20your%20real%20email%20address%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch4%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2211025a59-7d93-486c-a783-6dc1de07a058%5C%22%3EProvider%20aliases%20(multiple%20addresses%2C%20one%20inbox)%3C%2Fh4%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20most%20often%20seen%20in%20business.%20For%20example%2C%20when%20you%20get%20in%20touch%20with%20a%20company%2C%20and%20they%20have%20an%20address%20like%20info%40%20or%20press%40%2C%20these%20are%20examples%20of%20provider%20aliases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20specific%20addresses%20linked%20to%20the%20same%20account%2C%20letting%20you%20give%20out%20different%20versions%20of%20your%20email%20to%20those%20who%20need%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20can%20be%20useful%20if%20you%20use%20your%20email%20for%20both%20public%20and%20private%20uses%2C%20such%20as%20a%20business%20side%20and%20a%20personal%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20services%20can%20put%20limits%20on%20how%20many%20of%20these%20you%20can%20generate.%20Also%2C%20like%20%2B%20aliases%20above%2C%20these%20are%20still%20closely%20tied%20to%20you%2C%20and%20people%20can%20reverse-engineer%20them%20to%20find%20your%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch4%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229abd9c36-675e-4396-a0d8-7bd94d7ea96b%5C%22%3EMasked%2Fforwarding%20aliases%3C%2Fh4%3E%3Cp%3EMasked%20or%20forwarding%20aliases%20are%20all%20about%20security%20and%20privacy.%20The%20idea%20is%20simple%3A%20you%20generate%20a%20completely%20random%20email%20address%2C%20but%20anything%20sent%20to%