EPut%20simply%2C%20if%20you%20wouldn't%20want%20an%20email%20from%20them%20in%20a%20year%2C%20consider%20an%20alias.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222466d9d2-aa75-4f23-917f-884bf2766d01%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20start%20using%20email%20aliases%20in%205%20minutes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEmail%20aliases%20can%20seem%20daunting%2C%20but%20they're%20actually%20very%20easy%20to%20get%20started%20with.%20Realistically%2C%20you%20can%20get%20them%20set%20up%20in%20just%20five%20minutes%20with%20a%20few%20easy%20steps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirstly%2C%20pick%20your%20main%20inbox.%20This%20is%20where%20emails%20from%20the%20aliases%20will%20come%20in%2C%20so%20it%20is%20best%20to%20use%20your%20core%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20choose%20your%20email%20alias%20method%20from%20the%20three%20mentioned%20above%20(plus%2C%20provider%20and%20masked).%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15118297617va-20%26h%3Dfc73eccc0c4e0fece21dc5e7e497a34a7930389a3307c24255f27e8dad7a78f8%26postID%3D69c189225ebd47b37dfd7714%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fwhat-is-an-email-alias%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fproton.me%252Fmail%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EProton%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20solid%20option%20if%20you%20want%20to%20try%20out%20the%20latter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20here%2C%20start%20with%20two%20to%20three%20categories%20to%20set%20up%20an%20alias%20for.%20These%20could%20be%20shopping%2C%20newsletters%2C%20accounts%2C%20etc.%20Choosing%20specific%20categories%20stops%20things%20from%20getting%20too%20messy%20too%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20set%20up%20a%20filter%2Flabel%20system%20for%20these%20new%20aliases%20straight%20away.%20This%20will%20make%20the%20system%20feel%20instantly%20actionable%20as%20you%20watch%20specific%20emails%20filter%20out%20of%20your%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20and%20very%20importantly%2C%20save%20a%20quick%20note%20of%20which%20ali