0boarding%20school%20in%20China%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-education-public-school-children-chinese-elite-colleges-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20Business%20Insider%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20arrangement%2C%20records%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20status%20of%20the%20probe%20that%20began%20in%20late%202023%20is%20unclear.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faudit-val-verde-pegasus-school-china-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehighly%20critical%20audit%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20also%20prompted%20by%20Business%20Insider's%20reporting%20and%20released%20last%20week%20by%20state%20education%20authorities%2C%20has%20been%20referred%20to%20the%20local%20district%20attorney.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-education-public-school-children-chinese-elite-colleges-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider's%202021%20investigation%3C%2Fa%3E%20brought%20attention%20to%20the%20cozy%20relationship%20between%20the%20Val%20Verde%20Unified%20School%20District%2C%20top%20current%20and%20former%20state%20education%20officials%2C%20and%20Pegasus%20California%20School%2C%20a%20private%20school%20in%20Qingdao%2C%20China%2C%20that%20charges%20students%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20a%20year%20in%20tuition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELess%20than%20a%20week%20after%20the%20story%20was%20published%2C%20the%20Riverside%20County%20Office%20of%20Education%20contacted%20the%20Fiscal%20Crisis%20and%20Management%20Assistant%20Team%2C%20a%20state%20agency%2C%20to%20conduct%20an%20audit%20of%20the%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECounty%20education%20officials%20later%20said%20in%20court%20papers%20that%20they%20were%20concerned%20that%20diplomas%20issued%20by%20Val%20Verde%20to%20Pegasus%20students%20violated%20state%20code%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20that%20there%20may%20have%20been%20fraud%2C%20misappropriation%20of%20funds%2C%20or%20other%20illegal%20fiscal%20practices%26quot%3B%20associated%20with%20the%20partnership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20diploma%20for%20Pegasus%20California%20School%20graduates%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69bc987075bee4e0ee55e41b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221934%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20copy%20of%20the%20Pegasus%20California%20School%20diploma%20shows%20that%20it%20was%20issued%20by%20the%20Val%20Verde%20Unified%20School%20District.%3Cp%3EVerde%20Unified%20School%20District%20via%20records%20request%3B%20Samantha%20Lee%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Riverside%20office%20sued%20FCMAT%20in%20May%202024%2C%20alleging%20its%20investigation%20was%20shoddy.%20Court%20papers%20reveal%20that%20it%20also%20referred%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20US%20Attorney's%20Office%20for%20the%20Central%20District%20of%20California%20%26quot%3Bso%20that%20it%2C%20and%20other%20federal%20agencies%2C%20would%20investigate%20the%20Pegasus%20Diploma%20Program%20for%20potential%20criminal%20prosecution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20May%202024%2C%20the%20investigation%20was%20active%2C%20with%20a%20county%20education%20official%20interviewed%20a%20month%20earlier%2C%20the%20suit%20says.%20Ciaran%20McEvoy%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20federal%20prosecutors'%20office%2C%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20whether%20it's%20still%20open.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlex%20Sponheim%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Val%20Verde%2C%20said%20that%20the%20district%20was%20never%20contacted%20by%20the%20Justice%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202025%2C%20a%20judge%20ordered%20that%20FCMAT's%20reports%20into%20Pegasus%20stay%20under%20wraps%20after%20the%20Riverside%20County%20Office%20of%20Education%20argued%20the%20%26quot%3Bsurface-level%20investigation%26quot%3B%20could%20%26quot%3Bnegatively%20impact%26quot%3B%20further%20investigations%20into%20potential%20misconduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20month%20later%2C%20the%20office%20retained%20the%20Los%20Angeles-based%20law%20firm%20Larson%20LLP%20to%20examine%20the%20ties%20between%20Val%20Verde%20and%20Pegasus.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faudit-val-verde-pegasus-school-china-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThat%20scathing%20audit%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20%26quot%3Bsufficient%20evidence%26quot%3B%20of%20%26quot%3Bfraud%2C%20misappropriation%20of%20funds%2C%20or%20other%20illegal%20fiscal%20practices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStephen%20Larson%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20Larson%20LLP%20and%20the%20author%20of%20the%20report%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20the%20audit%20%26quot%3Braises%20serious%20concerns%20about%20academic%20integrity%2C%20taxpayer%20fraud%2C%20and%20may%20even%20implicate%20national%20security.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20found%20that%20a%20California%20public%20school%20district%20improperly%20issued%20diplomas%20to%20students%20in%20China%2C%26quot%3B%20Larson%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20broader%20record%20shows%20those%20California%20credentials%20may%20have%20been%20used%20to%20create%20false%20legitimacy%20for%20students%20seeking%20entry%20into%20American%20universities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Flags%20outside%20the%20Pegasus%20California%20School%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c2f1df58b5806618e7df6f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221601%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20state%20flag%20of%20California%20flew%20outside%20of%20Pegasus.%3Cp%3EYan%20Cong%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20diploma%20program%20was%20halted%2C%20but%20Pegasus%20remains%20open%20and%2C%20according%20to%20its%20website%2C%20is%20accredited%20by%20the%20nonprofit%20organization%20Cognia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20audit%20said%20the%20Western%20Association%20of%20Schools%20and%20Colleges%20wouldn't%20accredit%20Pegasus%20because%20it%20didn't%20meet%20its%20standards.%20Pegasus%20states%20on%20its%20site%20that%20it%20was%20founded%20%26quot%3Bwith%20the%20blessing%20and%20support%20of%20the%20California%20Department%20of%20Education.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECognia%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%20The%20California%20Department%20of%20Education%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faudit-val-verde-pegasus-school-china-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20told%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Bwill%20not%20stand%20for%20any%20misuse%20of%20public%20funds%20and%20supports%20any%20investigation%20into%20this%20matter.%20California%20diplomas%20are%20for%20California%20students.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Riverside%20County%20District%20Attorney's%20Office%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20it%20couldn't%20comment%20on%20possible%20investigative%20matters.%20A%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20State%20Controller's%20office%2C%20which%20oversees%20fiscal%20matters%20for%20the%20state%2C%20confirmed%20that%20their%20office%20had%20received%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20audit%20report%20and%20is%20reviewing%20it%20to%20determine%20appropriate%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aneinbinder%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eneinbinder%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%20at%20neinbinder.70.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20device%2C%20and%20nonwork%20WiFi%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsecure-news-tips%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%20to%2