com%2F69b4319aa7a4f9df67ba4ce9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20realized%20that%20using%20a%20CPAP%20machine%20was%20helping%20her.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20resisted%20my%20sleep%20apnea%20diagnosis%20and%20hated%20using%20my%20CPAP%20machine.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20avoided%20the%20full-face%20mask%20because%20I%20thought%20it%20meant%20failure.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOnce%20I%20found%20the%20right%20mask%2C%20my%20sleep%20and%20symptoms%20improved.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20done%20everything%20I%20could%20think%20of%20to%20not%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fhow-to-treat-sleep-apnea%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ediagnosed%20with%20sleep%20apnea%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Yet%20here%20I%20was%20at%2010%3A30%20p.m.%2C%20slamming%20shut%20the%20reservoir%20on%20my%20godforsaken%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fwhat-is-a-cpap-machine%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECPAP%20machine%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20stomping%20around%20my%20bedroom%20like%20a%20toddler.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20listening%20to%20me%20from%20downstairs%2C%20my%20husband%20entered%20our%20bedroom%20to%20try%20to%20have%20a%20grown-up%20conversation%20with%20me.%20I'm%20sure%20he%20began%20with%20something%20rational%20like%20asking%20if%20I%20was%20OK%2C%20and%20I%20probably%2C%20with%20sarcasm%2C%20asked%20him%20if%20I'd%20told%20him%20lately%20how%20much%20I%20hate%20my%20stupid%20machine.%20I%20wondered%20how%20he'd%20managed%20to%20survive%20using%20his%20for%20so%20many%20years%20while%20he%20tinkered%20with%20the%20settings%20on%20mine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e38b7183-7909-4ae0-b60c-235a71157fa0%5C%22%3EI%20didn't%20want%20to%20have%20another%20medical%20issue%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20I%20dealt%20head-on%20with%20physical%20problems%2C%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-medical-menopause-at-age-20-real-menopause-easier-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emedically%20induced%20menopause%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20a%20pulmonary%20embolism%2C%20and%20eventually%2C%20autoimmune%20disorders.%20When%20my%20husband%20kindly%20suggested%20perhaps%20my%20exhaustion%20and%20ever-worsening%20snoring%20could%20be%20sleep%20apnea%2C%20I%20gave%20him%20a%20resounding%3A%20nope.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20I%20acquiesced%20%E2%80%94%20mostly%20to%20prove%20him%20wrong.%20It%20turned%20out%20I%20was%20having%2014%20to%2019%20apnea%20episodes%20per%20hour.%20I%20decided%20that%20wasn't%20too%20bad%2C%20ignored%20the%20results%2C%20and%20kept%20on%20trucking%2C%20never%20feeling%20rested.%20In%20fact%2C%20despite%20being%20nearly%2010%20years%20out%20from%20surgical%20menopause%2C%20I%20still%20experienced%20eight%20or%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-treat-menopause-hot-flashes-vaginal-dryness-2019-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehot%20flashes%3C%2Fa%3E%20per%20day.%20I%20also%20woke%20up%20throughout%20the%20night%2C%20finding%20it%20increasingly%20difficult%20to%20fall%20back%20asleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20months%2C%20when%20my%20husband%20broached%20the%20subject%2C%20I%20shut%20down.%20I've%20had%20plenty%20of%20other%20health%20issues%2C%20so%20neither%20of%20us%20understood%20what%20was%20so%20different%20about%20this%20situation.%20Finally%2C%20though%2C%20it%20rose%20to%20the%20surface%3A%20I%20didn't%20want%20something%20else%20to%20be%20wrong%20with%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fdec8354-8398-4522-bf00-680ab9baa8e1%5C%22%3EI%20felt%20like%20a%20failure%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20I%20couldn't%20say%20out%20loud%20then%20but%20understood%20later%20was%20what%20I%20associated%20with%20a%20Continuous%20Positive%20Airway%20Pressure%20machine%3A%20failure.%20Further%20proof%20that%20I%20was%20overweight%2C%20aging%2C%20and%20not%20in%20great%20shape.%20Now%20I%20had%20to%20add%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foverweight-high-school-lost-hundred-pounds-in-college-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einability%20to%20breathe%20correctly%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20initially%20made%20me%20angry%2C%20and%20my%20bad%20attitude%20led%20to%20uninformed%20decisions.%20More%20concerned%20about%20how%20I'd%20look%2C%20even%20in%20the%20privacy%20of%20my%20own%20bedroom%2C%20I%20declined%20the%20online%20survey%20the%20company%20sent%20me%20that%20would%20have%20helped%20me%20realize%20the%20nasal%20pillow%20CPAP%20mask%20wasn't%20my%20best%20choice%20due%20to%20my%20seasonal%20allergies%20and%20a%20constant%20stuffy%20nose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20received%20my%20machine%20and%20mask%2C%20insurance%20required%20that%20I%20wear%20them%20for%20at%20least%20four%20hours%20a%20night%20for%2030%20of%20the%2090%20days.%20I%20wasn't%20off%20to%20a%20good%20start%20when%20the%20nasal%20pillows%20made%20me%20feel%20like%20I%20was%20suffocating%2C%20and%20I%20took%20the%20mask%20off%20in%20my%20sleep%20every%20night.%20I%20woke%20each%20morning%20with%20a%20raging%20sinus%20headache.%20Lousy%20luck%20continued%20that%20first%20month%2C%20as%20I%20ended%20up%20with%20both%20a%20tooth%20and%20a%20sinus%20infection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20healed%2C%20I%20needed%20a%20new%20mask.%20Again%2C%20I%20declined%20the%20survey%2C%20because%20%E2%80%94%20I%20don't%20know.%20OK%2C%20I%20do%20know.%20I%20was%20convinced%20the%20full-face%20mask%20was%20the%20least%20sophisticated%20choice.%20I%20might%20be%20old%2C%20but%20I%20could%20still%20try%20to%20be%20somewhat%20cool.%20The%20next%20one%2C%20however%2C%20a%20small%20hybrid%20nasal%20pillow%20and%20mouth%20mask%2C%20didn't%20work%20at%20all.%20Not%20even%20for%20a%20night.%20That%20was%20it.%20I%20didn't%20care%20anymore.%20I'd%20rather%20have%20sleep%20apnea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20then%2C%20I%20was%20six%20weeks%20into%20my%2090%20days.%20I%20let%20myself%20not%20care%20for%20another%20week%2C%20until%20my%20husband%20asked%20if%20we'd%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20my%20machine.%20Suddenly%20I%20cared%20a%20lot.%20When%20I%20called%20the%20company%2C%20they%20again%20suggested%20the%20survey%20they'd%20sent%20me%20(three%20times).%20Finally%2C%20I%20took%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20I%20should%20use%20the%20traditional%2C%20full-face%20mask.%20Of%20course%20I%20should.%20Out%20of%20sheer%20exhaustion%2C%20I%20got%20over%20myself.%20I%20was%20overweight%20and%20getting%20older.%20I%20was%20not%20cool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22357820d8-89d9-4dd0-a2a1-945a85f079f5%5C%22%3EI%20finally%20was%20sleeping%20through%20the%20night%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20later%2C%20the%20mask%20arrived.%20As%20soon%20as%20I%20put%20it%20on%2C%20I%20knew.%20It%20was%20the%20one.%20Unlike%20the%20hybrid%2C%20this%20fit%20my%20face%20perfectly%2C%20and%20without%20nasal%20pillows%2C%20my%20stuffy%20nose%20didn't%20feel%20like%20it%20was%20trying%20to%20suffocate%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20I%20remained%20unconvinced%20of%20CPAP's%20efficacy.%20On%20a%20drive%20with%20my%20mom%20months%20later%2C%20I%20grumpily%20listed%20its%20downsides%3A%20I%20wasn't%20bounding%20through%20life%20with%20new%20energy.%20I%20hadn't%20lost%20weight.%20I%20still%20had%20migraines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20longer%20I%20talked%20to%20her%20that%20day%2C%20however%2C%20the%20more%20I%20noticed%20small%20areas%20that%20seemed%20to%20be%20improving.%20The%20first%2C%20and%20most%20notable%2C%20was%20that%20I'd%20been%20sleeping%20through%20the%20night.%20I%20guess%20I%20had%20to%20admit%20it%20was%20helping.%20A%20little.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20even%20more%20has%20changed.%20I%20have%20fewer%20hot%20flashes%2C%20and%20sometimes%20I%20even%20feel%20well-rested.%20Now%2C%20when%20people%20ask%2C%20I%20don't%20hesitate%20to%20tell%20them%20I%20have%20sleep%20apnea%2C%20I%20wear%20a%20full%20face%20mask%2C%20and%20I%20no%20longer%20hate%20my%20little%20breathing%20machine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frefused-cpap-machine-sleep-apnea-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774385221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b4319aa7a4f9df67ba4ce9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frefused-cpap-machine-sleep-apnea-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20associated%20a%20CPAP%20machine%20with%20failure%2C%20aging%2C%20and%20being%20out%20of%20shape%2C%20but%20treating%20my%20sleep%20apnea%20transformed%20my%20sleep%20and%20overall%20health.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Stacey%20Danevicz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frefused-cpap-machine-sleep-apnea-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Emmy%20Winning%20Producer-Showrunner%20Charles%20Wachter%20Launches%20Stopwatch%20Media%20With%20The%20Mediapro%20Studio%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774384796000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236698271%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Madrid-based%20global%20powerhouse%20The%20Mediapro%20Studio%20has%20joined%20forces%20with%20Emmy-winning%20producer-showrunner%20Charles%20Wachter%20to%20launch%20a%20new%20non-fiction%20banner%2C%20Stopwatch%20Media.%20Wachter%2C%20whose%20notable%20credits%20include%20reality%20shows%20%E2%80%9CMillion%20Dollar%20Secret%E2%80%9D%C2%A0for%20Netflix%2C%C2%A0%E2%80%9CBeast%20Games%E2%80%9D%20for%20Prime%20V%C3%ADdeo%20and%20%E2%80%9CGot%20to%20Get%20Out%E2%80%9D%20for%20Hulu%2C%20as%20well%20as%20hit%20Netflix%20series%20%E2%80%9CWin%20the%20Mall%2C%E2%80%9D%20will%20be%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Anna%20Marie%20de%20la%20Fuente%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdn